<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1825077-as-a-first-time-reader-of-you-as-an">As a first time reader of you as an author, which book would you start with?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1825077'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F769896.Poland">like</a></span>

