<div id="review_2575988706" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2575988706" />
    <a title="Rebecca" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/37142297-rebecca"><img alt="Rebecca" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2575988706?book_show_action=true">Oct 28, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rebecca" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rebecca" href="/user/show/37142297-rebecca">Rebecca</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2575988706" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15455602681336777531">I thought I would never make it through the first 100 pages, but I am glad I stuck with it. This book is so well-researched, and so real. Once I got through the first 100 pages, which I felt went slowly, and into the war, and the struggle of it all, wow. Just wow. This book was incredible. <br/><br/>No spoilers here, there is too much to say. I am so glad to have read this one. Exceptional. </span>

          </span>
